#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/3.0/guides/http-reference.adoc:20
msgid "This document explains various HTTP features that you can use in Quarkus."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/3.0/guides/http-reference.adoc:24
